 Coverage: We tested the JSON parser, the Regex fallback, the PDF reader, and the App navigation.\
\ls6\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
 Automation: We linked these tests to GitHub Actions.\
